author: Mark Sandritter
title: 15-year-old Fran Belibi becomes first girl to dunk in Colorado high school history
text:
First Colorado HS Girls Dunk in history. Fran Belibi 15 yr old soph Regis Jesuit HS #SCtop10 @milehimagicbb @MileHiSptsPreps @MileHighSports pic.twitter.com/bMPoRJyPfe 
— Regis HS Girls Bball (@RJHSGDBball) January 7, 2017 Meet Fran Belibi. She is a 15-year-old high school sophomore who just made Colorado history. Belibi stole a pass at midcourt and then was off to the races. She didn’t just become the first girl in Colorado high school history, but she did it emphatically with a one-handed crush.
Defenders in Colorado now need to keep their heads on a swivel to avoid getting posterized by Belibi.
